# ── Proprietary SR Research files (EyeLink SDK) ──────────────────────────────
# CalibrationGraphicsPygame.py and audio assets are distributed with the
# EyeLink Developers Kit and may NOT be redistributed.
# Obtain them from: https://www.sr-support.com/
eye_tracking_library/CalibrationGraphicsPygame.py
eye_tracking_library/__pycache__/
eye_tracking_library/*.wav
eye_tracking_library/*.pyc

# ── RTBox driver (no open-source license) ────────────────────────────────────
# Obtain from: https://github.com/xiangruili/RTBox_py
button_box_library/RTBox.py
button_box_library/__pycache__/
button_box_library/*.pyc

# ── InpOut32 binaries ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Obtain from: https://www.highrez.co.uk/downloads/inpout32/
biopac_input_library/*.dll

# ── PyGaze mpydev.py (GPL v3 — incompatible with MIT) ────────────────────────
# Kept locally as a reference only; see biopac_library/README.md
biopac_library/mpydev.py

# ── BIOPAC mpdev.dll is system-installed, never in the repo ──────────────────
# Install: BIOPAC Hardware API 2.2 Research from https://www.biopac.com/

